These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, indonesian, pakistani, colombian, canadian, chinese, german
1. the indonesian is in the middle##1
2. the indonesian is on the left of the pakistani##1
3. the canadian is on the right of the colombian##1
4. the turkish is on the right of the pakistani##1
5. the german is on the far left##1
6. the chinese is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | german | colombian | canadian | indonesian | pakistani | turkish | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  chef, bartender, architect, journalist, freelancer, coach, firefighter
1. the firefighter is on the far right##1
2. the chef is on the far left##1
3. the chef is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the freelancer is on the left of the architect##1
5. the journalist is on the right of the coach##1
6. the firefighter is on the right of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | chef | freelancer | architect | coach | journalist | bartender | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: gardening, skydiving, hiking, reading, photography, filmmaking, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | photography | gardening | filmmaking | hiking | cooking | skydiving | reading |

 #################################

 
