1. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | dog | rat | cat | horse | fish | frog | hamster |

